scene.message:
Man in black: Don't make us{nl}
repeat ourselves. Beyond here{nl}
is under Sebek control.{nl}
Disobey and we shoot.{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: That dumb idiot!{nl}
He's gonna get himself{nl}
killed!{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Heh heh, sorry 'bout{nl}
him, he ain't quite right.{nl}
C'mon, blockhead, move it.{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Well now...{nl}
Even you help people?{nl}
Truly a bolt from the blue.{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Idiot.{nl}
Even a guy like that's got{nl}
a mom who'd cry if he died.{waitkey}{ret}

Man in black: This is no place{nl}
for kids. Get out of here{nl}
and find shelter.{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Sebek...{nl}
Kamitori, what are you{nl}
scheming?{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: I don't like this...{nl}
So they're more than just{nl}
a company.{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: What on earth is{nl}
going on? I thought SEBEC{nl}
was a top-tier company...{waitkey}{nl}
No different from the Mafia.{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: Oh?{nl}
Isn't that the transfer{nl}
student over there?{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Hm?{nl}
Hey, that's Kido, ain't it?{nl}
What's he doin' there?{waitkey}{ret}

{color:2}Kido Reiji{nl}
A student who transferred{nl}
here half a year ago.{nl}
Quiet, always acts alone.{color:0}{waitkey}{ret}

Man in black: Who are you?{nl}
This area is under Sebek{nl}
control. Entry is forbidden.{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Hey, Sebek — that's{nl}
Sonoda's mom's company,{nl}
right? What's going on!?{waitkey}{ret}
